WEBVTT

00:02.769 --> 00:04.136
¶ Just sit right back ¶

00:04.204 --> 00:05.537
¶ and you'll hear a tale ¶

00:05.606 --> 00:07.673
¶ a tale of a fateful trip ¶

00:07.741 --> 00:09.842
¶ that started
from this tropic port ¶

00:09.910 --> 00:12.210
¶ aboard this tiny ship ¶

00:12.279 --> 00:14.713
¶ the mate was
a mighty sailin' man ¶

00:14.782 --> 00:17.149
¶ the skipper
brave and sure ¶

00:17.217 --> 00:19.351
¶ 5 passengers
set sail that day ¶

00:19.420 --> 00:21.720
¶ for a 3-hour tour ¶

00:21.789 --> 00:24.623
¶ a 3-hour tour ¶

00:24.691 --> 00:26.624
[thunder]

00:26.693 --> 00:28.827
¶ The weather
started getting rough ¶

00:28.896 --> 00:31.363
¶ the tiny ship was tossed ¶

00:31.432 --> 00:33.598
¶ if not for the courage
of the fearless crew ¶

00:33.667 --> 00:35.768
¶ the <i> minnow</i>
would be lost ¶

00:35.836 --> 00:38.303
¶ the <i> minnow</i>
would be lost ¶

00:38.372 --> 00:39.938
¶ the ship set ground
on the shore ¶

00:40.007 --> 00:42.974
¶ of this uncharted
desert isle ¶

00:43.043 --> 00:45.343
¶ with gilligan ¶

00:45.412 --> 00:47.779
¶ the skipper, too ¶

00:47.848 --> 00:49.748
¶ the millionaire ¶

00:49.816 --> 00:52.050
¶ and his wife ¶

00:52.119 --> 00:54.953
¶ the movie star ¶

00:55.021 --> 00:56.755
¶ and the rest ¶

00:56.824 --> 01:02.194
¶ are here
on gilligan's isle ¶

